{
  "stem": "26276.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because most of the Jewish stores-- most were Jewish stores.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the gentiles-- they knew that they have to prepare the food, the bread enough to last them over like, Passover.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they had to buy for seven days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Otherwise, the ones who baked, they could bake their own.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Otherwise, the stores would be closed to buy flour even.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well, he was a contractor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most of the stuff that he made-- I  remember sometimes-- so I delivered it on a little wagon to the stores.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So most of it was like, contracting to the stores.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that  I went to school together, or they lived around my neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Good.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't until the last minute.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That happ-- that happened one day in 1939.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came home from school late in the-- late in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People started to talk that we're not going to be able to sleep home that night, that we are going to have to hide in shelters, because they heard that the Germans are very close by.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Across the street from us lived one of my uncles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in that house, he had a big basement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When dark came around, my parents took the whole family across the street to sleep in the basement there, because we didn't have that basement.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And during the night, we heard louder noises-- guns, you know, like from tanks-- shootings-- bombarding.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And everybody curled up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it went on like this until daylight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Daylight came around.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everybody was anxious to see what's going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They opened up a little doors to look out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And what we did see was turned over tanks in the streets, a lot of dead soldiers laying in the streets.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
